items.name: Exalted Small SPACE
items.description: SPACE are expansions to your Personal Metaverse that come in different sizes and rarities. SPACE is needed to attach Utility NFTs such as Armories, Forges and Time Wardens that allow you to craft and upgrade cosmetic NFTs and Hourglasses. SPACE can also be decorated with NFTs that you will find in game. You can connect multiple SPACE together to customize the layout of your Personal Metaverse. A Small Exalted SPACE has 3 Exits that can be used to connect to other SPACE or Utility NFTs.

SPACE is needed to attach Utility NFTs such as Armories, Forges and Time Wardens that allow you to craft and upgrade cosmetic NFTs and Hourglasses. SPACE can also be decorated with NFTs that you will find in game. You can connect multiple SPACE together to customize the layout of your Personal Metaverse. A Medium Rare SPACE has 3 Exits that can be used to connect to other SPACE or Utility NFTs.

SPACE is needed to attach Utility NFTs such as Armories, Forges and Time Wardens that allow you to craft and upgrade cosmetic NFTs and Hourglasses. SPACE can also be decorated with NFTs that you will find in game. You can connect multiple SPACE together to customize the layout of your Personal Metaverse. A Medium Rare SPACE has 3 Exits that can be used to connect to other SPACE or Utility NFTs.
